about.summary: Easy access to the EPSG database via http://epsg.io/

name: pyepsg
raw_recipe:
{% set version = "0.3.1" %}

package:
  name: pyepsg
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: pyepsg-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url: https://github.com/rhattersley/pyepsg/archive/v{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: e278656ad5fbe5ec97d08f690fa18b3d9149e842b4c6f383409aee5c5e8bf528

build:
  number: 0
  script: python setup.py install --single-version-externally-managed --record record.txt

requirements:
  build:
    - python
    - setuptools
  run:
    - python
    - requests

test:
  imports:
    - pyepsg

about:
  home: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/pyepsg
  license: LGPL-3.0
  license_file: COPYING.LESSER
  summary: 'Easy access to the EPSG database via http://epsg.io/'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - pelson
    - rhattersley
    - ocefpaf
